        {
            "id": 6421276,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數上漲733.44點至37029.56點，漲幅2.02%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間15日09:57，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲733.44點（或2.02%），暫報37029.56點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+9.23%</li><li>近 1 月：+8.67%</li><li>近 3 月：+17.3%</li><li>近 6 月：+35.47%</li><li>今年以來：+25.32%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>SDN概念領漲+3.78%。其中    華星光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)            上漲        9.9%            ;        智邦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>)            上漲        8.47%            ;        眾達-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>)            上漲        4.24%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>散裝航運概念領漲+3.10%。其中    中航(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2612:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2612\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2612-TW</a>)            上漲        6.81%            ;        裕民(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2606:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2606\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2606-TW</a>)            上漲        4.98%            ;        慧洋-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2637:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2637\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2637-TW</a>)            上漲        3.28%    。</p></section></main>",
